snippet.title: Fortnite Complete 'Indiana Jones' Quests Guide - How to Unlock All Indiana Jones Rewards
snippet.description:
All Indiana Jones Challenges Guide - Fortnite Chapter 3 Season 3 - How to Unlock All Indiana Jones Rewards Guide and the Temple Explorer Outfit Style. How to Complete All Indiana Jones Quests Guide & How to Unlock Free Rewards. Support a creator code: Score (#ad).

You can become a member of my channel to gain access to exclusive perks!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrCz0Ffd83Z_eJ57A2We-Lg/join

Fortnite Chapter 3 Season 3 Challenges Guide Playlist ► 

...

———

Fortnite Chapter 3 Season 3 - All Indiana Jones Quests

0:00 - Use the Grapple Glove to Swing Off Trees (10)
1:02 - Collect the Durrrburger Relic from The Temple and The Ruins in a Single Match (2)
1:40 - Raider's Relics Pickaxe & Expedition Bag Back Bling Reward
1:52 - Damage Opponents While Riding in or Standing on a Vehicle (500)
3:03 - Search Chests at Shifty Shafts (5)
4:19 - Indiana Jones Outfit Reward
4:28 - Find the Secret Door Past the Main Chamber in Shuffled Shrines (1)
6:30 - Stash an Item of Mythic or Exotic Rarity in a Tent (1)
7:21 - Indy's Escape Spray Reward
7:26 - Make Runaway Boulders Roll for 100 Meters in a Single Match (100)
7:59 - Damage Opponents with a Pistol (750)
8:48 - Place Top 5 in a Match (1)
9:36 - Doctor Jones Emoticon, Indiana Jones Temple Explorer Outfit Style, First Misadventure Loading Screen, & Emergency Raft Glider Rewards

Fortnite Chapter 3 Season 3 - All Island Hopper Quest Rewards

Check out Fortnite.GG for Spawn Locations, Giveaways, Item Shop Updates and much more! https://fortnite.gg/?ps

———

UNLOCK WORLD FAMOUS ARCHAEOLOGIST INDIANA JONES IN THE FORTNITE CHAPTER 3 SEASON 3 BATTLE PASS!

7.6.2022
By The Fortnite Team

You’ve heard a lot about him, now get ready to unlock him! Complete Indiana JonesTM’  Battle Pass Quests starting now to unlock his Outfit and more items from the Indiana Jones Set. All the Quests — and each one’s rewards — can be uncovered below.

PAGE 1 OF THE INDIANA JONES QUESTS
Complete the Page 1 Quests below (in any order) to unlock the Indiana Jones Outfit!

SEARCH 5 CHESTS AT SHIFTY SHAFTS
Take the left tunnel. NO, the LEFT tunnel! Unlocks an Indiana Jones Banner.

DO 500 DAMAGE TO OPPONENTS WHILE RIDING IN OR STANDING ON A VEHICLE
It's not the years. It's the mileage. Unlocks the Rogue Archaeology Wrap.

USE THE GRAPPLE GLOVE TO SWING OFF TREES 10 TIMES
You know how to fly, don't you? Unlocks the Raider's Relics Pickaxe.

COLLECT THE DURRRBURGER RELIC FROM THE TEMPLE AND THE RUINS IN A SINGLE MATCH
It belongs in a museum. Unlocks the Expedition Bag Back Bling.

The Indiana Jones Outfit, Indiana Jones Banner, Rogue Archaeology Wrap, Raider’s Relics Pickaxe, and Expedition Bag Back Bling.

For completing all of the Quests on Page 1, you’ll unlock Page 2 of the Indiana Jones Quests!

PAGE 2 OF THE INDIANA JONES QUESTS 
Complete the Page 2 Quests below (in any order) to unlock the Temple Explorer Style of the Indiana Jones Outfit!

FIND THE SECRET DOOR PAST THE MAIN CHAMBER IN SHUFFLED SHRINES
Don’t worry, there aren’t any snakes. Unlocks the built-in Indy's Dustoff Emote for the Indiana Jones Outfit.

STASH AN ITEM OF MYTHIC OR EXOTIC RARITY IN A TENT
Time to get some fortune and glory. Unlocks the Indy's Escape Spray.

MAKE RUNAWAY BOULDERS ROLL FOR 100 METERS IN A SINGLE MATCH
You call THIS archaeology? Unlocks the Doctor Jones Emoticon.

DO 750 DAMAGE TO OPPONENTS WITH A PISTOL
“Trust me.” Unlocks the First Misadventure Loading Screen.

FINISH TOP 5 IN A MATCH
Just make it up as you go. Unlocks the Emergency Raft Glider.

The Indy’s Dustoff Emote, Indy’s Escape Spray, Doctor Jones Emoticon, First Misadventure Loading Screen, and Emergency Raft Glider.
 
If you own the Chapter 3 Season 3 Battle Pass, the Indiana Jones Quests are available now in the “Quests” page. The Quests are available for the whole rest of the Season!

Source: https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/en-US/news/unlock-world-famous-archaeologist-indiana-jones-in-the-fortnite-chapter-3-season-3-battle-pass

———

Twitter  https://twitter.com/scoretrics

For completing all of the Quests on Page 1, you’ll unlock Page 2 of the Indiana Jones Quests!

PAGE 2 OF THE INDIANA JONES QUESTS 
Complete the Page 2 Quests below (in any order) to unlock the Temple Explorer Style of the Indiana Jones Outfit!

FIND THE SECRET DOOR PAST THE MAIN CHAMBER IN SHUFFLED SHRINES
Don’t worry, there aren’t any snakes. Unlocks the built-in Indy's Dustoff Emote for the Indiana Jones Outfit.

STASH AN ITEM OF MYTHIC OR EXOTIC RARITY IN A TENT
Time to get some fortune and glory. Unlocks the Indy's Escape Spray.

MAKE RUNAWAY BOULDERS ROLL FOR 100 METERS IN A SINGLE MATCH
You call THIS archaeology? Unlocks the Doctor Jones Emoticon.

DO 750 DAMAGE TO OPPONENTS WITH A PISTOL
“Trust me.” Unlocks the First Misadventure Loading Screen.

FINISH TOP 5 IN A MATCH
Just make it up as you go. Unlocks the Emergency Raft Glider.

The Indy’s Dustoff Emote, Indy’s Escape Spray, Doctor Jones Emoticon, First Misadventure Loading Screen, and Emergency Raft Glider.
 
If you own the Chapter 3 Season 3 Battle Pass, the Indiana Jones Quests are available now in the “Quests” page. The Quests are available for the whole rest of the Season!
